    <item>
      <title>4C FCPdf External Library - Most Recent Changes</title>
      <link>https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/fcpdfchanges/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/fcpdfchanges/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/&#34;&gt;4C External Libraries Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/&#34;&gt;FCPdf Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;05 September 2025&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;05-september-2025&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#05-september-2025&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;There is a new funtion that makes it easier to split a long text into multiple lines and format it as a block of text within a specified rectangle. The function is &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/functions/textrect/&#34;&gt;TextRect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;28 July 2020&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;28-july-2020&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#28-july-2020&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The following 4 functions now have an optional final argument that allows specifying and encoding for the font being selected. This is most useful when using a UTF-8 font. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/functions/docsetfontface/&#34;&gt;DocSetFontFace&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/functions/docsetfont/&#34;&gt;DocSetFont&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/functions/pagesetfontface/&#34;&gt;PageSetFontFace&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashish-kus/4C_docs/docs/features/extlibs/fcpdf/functions/pagesetfont/&#34;&gt;PageSetFont&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;05 February 2018&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;05-february-2018&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#05-february-2018&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;True Type and Type 1 fonts are supported.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;15 January 2018&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;15-january-2018&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#15-january-2018&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initial Release and Documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
